OL,3,GNorth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA cloudy start for many,
OL,6,Fespecially on higher ground where
OL,7,Fthere could be some light drizzle.
OL,8,FFeeling much fresher than of late with
OL,9,Fbright or sunny spells developing into
OL,10,Fthe afternoon. Breezy along the coast
OL,11,Fand over the hills.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FClearer skies for many
OL,14,Fovernight which will allow
OL,15,Ftemperatures to fall, giving a much
OL,16,Fmore comfortable night for many.
OL,17,FStaying dry with mist and fog in
OL,18,Fplaces.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
