OL,2,W+.-'"-$/*%*%*%/"-$/*%Q,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,3,GNorth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CSaturday:FA bright start under some
OL,6,Fhigh cloud, sunny spells turning hazy.
OL,7,FRain moving in from the west during
OL,8,Fthe late afternoon, can be heavy at
OL,9,Ftimes. Remains warm.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Sunday to Tuesday:FSunday
OL,12,Fsees more rain and cloud with some
OL,13,Fsunny spells. Continuing into Monday
OL,14,Fwith heavy showers, possible
OL,15,Fthunderstorms. Staying unsettled
OL,16,Fthrough the week as temperatures
OL,17,Freturn to average.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
